WEBVTT

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.350
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:13.430
joining us again tonight. We're

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:14.910
going to go ahead and pray,

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:17.350
take communion like we always

00:00:17.360 --> 00:00:19.910
do, and worship a

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:22.390
little bit. We'll sing some songs and

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:25.150
just flow with the Holy Spirit

00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:28.030
here to see what He has for us. I want

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:30.150
to go over some things the Lord has

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.150
been talking to me about; it's

00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:34.750
been on my heart—a lot about the

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:37.350
prophetic and all the

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.310
chatter on the news right

00:00:39.320 --> 00:00:41.950
now: the internet, X, all of it,

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:44.670
from the alien stuff to

00:00:44.670 --> 00:00:44.680
everything else

00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:50.590
going on.

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:52.350
We're in a time like we've never seen

00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:55.790
before. Obviously, as everyone can see,

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:58.110
the signs of the times are unfolding all

00:00:58.120 --> 00:01:00.910
around us. I truly believe with all my

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:03.150
heart that Jesus Christ is coming sooner

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:04.430
than later.

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:06.190
He's coming back for His

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:07.750
glorious church.

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:09.510
Now,

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:11.870
there's so much chatter and so many

00:01:11.880 --> 00:01:14.630
voices. There's more prophetic

00:01:14.630 --> 00:01:14.640
activity

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:16.590
now than ever before because there's so

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.750
much access to it through the

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:19.910
internet.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:23.190
But I really want you to get

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:28.310
rooted in this: Romans 8:14.

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:30.790
You need to know:

00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:33.830
'For as many as are led

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:37.270
by the Spirit of God, they are the sons

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:39.110
and daughters of God.'The text

00:01:39.110 --> 00:01:39.120
says 'sons,'but

00:01:39.120 --> 00:01:41.070
I'll add 'daughters'as

00:01:41.070 --> 00:01:41.080
well because

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:43.590
it's for

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:45.350
the whole Body of Christ.

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:47.190
It's for every believer who

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:49.190
has

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.070
confessed Jesus Christ as their Lord

00:01:51.080 --> 00:01:52.590
and Savior.

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:55.390
Every one of us is led by the Spirit of

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.230
God.

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:58.230
We're not led by prophets anymore like

00:01:58.240 --> 00:02:01.390
they were in the Old Testament;

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:03.710
we're led by the Spirit of God. Now, God

00:02:03.720 --> 00:02:06.550
will use prophetic voices and prophecy

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:09.590
to confirm things you already

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:11.510
feel in your heart,

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.590
but it's not meant for you to get off into

00:02:13.590 --> 00:02:13.600
'weirdoville'and

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:15.630
follow everyone who calls

00:02:15.630 --> 00:02:15.640
themselves

00:02:15.640 --> 00:02:19.230
a prophet on YouTube, X, or whatever.

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:21.630
You are led by the Spirit of God, and you

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:24.030
need to understand that the Holy Spirit

00:02:24.040 --> 00:02:26.430
dwells inside of you.

00:02:26.440 --> 00:02:30.350
If every voice on YouTube, X, or Facebook goes away

00:02:30.350 --> 00:02:30.360
and

00:02:34.030 --> 00:02:34.040
you

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:36.870
ask,

00:02:36.880 --> 00:02:38.910
'Well, what do I do now?'you

00:02:38.910 --> 00:02:38.920
still

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:41.710
have that still, small voice

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:44.030
inside you. The Holy Spirit is

00:02:44.040 --> 00:02:46.310
speaking so loudly, and He talks all the

00:02:46.320 --> 00:02:47.470
time.

00:02:47.480 --> 00:02:50.390
He will lead you into all truth.

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:52.949
As you read the Word

00:02:52.959 --> 00:02:55.230
of God and get its

00:02:55.230 --> 00:02:55.240
foundation down

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:57.630
inside of your heart—you must read the

00:02:57.630 --> 00:02:57.640
Word—the

00:02:57.640 --> 00:03:01.150
Word will be a lamp unto your

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:03.949
feet and a light unto your path.

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:08.390
There's so much going on right

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:11.430
now that I want to drive home

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:14.190
this one

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:16.470
beautiful verse,

00:03:16.480 --> 00:03:19.790
Romans 8:14.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:21.590
If I don't say anything else to you

00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:24.030
tonight,

00:03:24.040 --> 00:03:26.390
you could take this verse and meditate

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:28.470
on it for the rest of the week, and it's

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:31.830
enough to sustain you:

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:33.870
'For as many

00:03:33.880 --> 00:03:37.470
as are led by the Spirit of God,

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:39.509
they are the sons and daughters of

00:03:40.830 --> 00:03:40.840
God.'I

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.590
want you to be

00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:47.870
rooted in that.

00:03:47.880 --> 00:03:49.910
You're led by the Spirit, not by

00:03:49.910 --> 00:03:49.920
the

00:03:49.920 --> 00:03:51.509
prophetic.

00:03:51.509 --> 00:03:51.519
Prophecy

00:03:51.519 --> 00:03:54.110
will

00:03:54.110 --> 00:03:54.120
confirm;

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:56.310
it exhorts

00:03:56.320 --> 00:03:59.270
and helps if you need

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:01.430
a little confirmation.

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:05.310
I don't believe Brandon

00:04:05.310 --> 00:04:05.320
Biggs—and

00:04:05.320 --> 00:04:07.350
I say this all the time

00:04:07.350 --> 00:04:07.360
when

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:08.910
people call me a

00:04:08.920 --> 00:04:10.390
prophet—I

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:12.550
believe I'm a watchman.

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:13.949
I believe God called me and said,

00:04:13.959 --> 00:04:15.630
'Brandon, I want you to go on YouTube

00:04:15.640 --> 00:04:17.390
and pray.

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:19.470
When you do this, I will show you

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:21.310
things to come.

00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:23.150
You'll pray about it, and

00:04:23.150 --> 00:04:23.160
some

00:04:23.160 --> 00:04:25.710
things will change while others will

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:26.909
not.

00:04:26.919 --> 00:04:29.070
But I want you to raise up a

00:04:29.070 --> 00:04:29.080
million-person

00:04:29.080 --> 00:04:31.990
prayer army of men

00:04:31.990 --> 00:04:32.000
and women.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.870
You'll pray for elections,

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:36.150
presidents, and things to

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:39.030
come. In doing so, the things

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:41.070
I show you will be seen on the news

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:43.670
and prove to be accurate.'Do I

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:45.909
miss it? I can;

00:04:45.919 --> 00:04:48.390
I'm just as human as everyone else.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:50.350
I don't label myself or have some big

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:52.110
banner calling myself 'Prophet Brandon

00:04:53.230 --> 00:04:53.240
Biggs.'I'm

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:58.870
just a person who said yes

00:04:58.870 --> 00:04:58.880
to

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:00.590
the

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:03.510
Lord.

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:05.190
In doing so, He's blessed me.

00:05:05.200 --> 00:05:08.070
It's been a very interesting

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.110
learning

00:05:10.110 --> 00:05:10.120
experience—from

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:12.110
the persecution to the

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.750
people who say they like you

00:05:13.760 --> 00:05:15.390
one minute and then don't the next.

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:18.470
You can't be swayed by that anymore. I

00:05:18.480 --> 00:05:20.710
have to realize that it's time to die.

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:24.790
Just like I was told by some elders:

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.270
'A dead man in

00:05:27.270 --> 00:05:27.280
a

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:29.470
coffin,

00:05:29.470 --> 00:05:29.480
Brandon—you

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:31.550
can yell at him and scream at him,

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:34.030
but he doesn't move. He has no emotion toward your screaming; that’s how you know he’s dead.'The moment you realize that it doesn't

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:45.230
matter how many

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:47.910
people scream at you, call

00:05:47.910 --> 00:05:47.920
you

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:49.790
false,

00:05:49.790 --> 00:05:49.800
or

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:51.870
are mean like

00:05:51.870 --> 00:05:51.880
a

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:53.550
school bully—it doesn't matter. I said, 'Lord,

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:55.270
I was bullied

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:58.630
all through school,

00:05:58.640 --> 00:06:00.830
and it was really

00:06:00.830 --> 00:06:00.840
bad.'It's

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.950
the same with adults

00:06:02.950 --> 00:06:02.960
and

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:04.910
cyberbullying.

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:06.630
The

00:06:06.640 --> 00:06:09.470
bullies in high school just grew

00:06:09.480 --> 00:06:11.470
up and are now the

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:14.350
bullies on the internet.

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:17.510
But we don't fear them; we fear

00:06:17.520 --> 00:06:18.909
God.

00:06:18.919 --> 00:06:20.270
The Lord said to

00:06:20.270 --> 00:06:20.280
me,

00:06:20.280 --> 00:06:22.030
'Do you fear man, Brandon?'I said,

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:24.070
'No, Lord, I fear

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:25.230
You.

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:27.070
I'll say what You want me to say, and

00:06:27.080 --> 00:06:28.710
if I'm wrong, You'll correct me along

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:29.670
the way.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:31.909
I do the best I

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:36.790
can.'I

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:43.909
try every time I go on here and

00:06:43.919 --> 00:06:46.310
pray with

00:06:46.310 --> 00:06:46.320
you.

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:49.510
If I miss it, I appreciate your grace

00:06:49.510 --> 00:06:49.520
as

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:51.310
we keep pushing on.

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:57.350
I want to bring it home to you

00:06:57.360 --> 00:07:00.230
all that you don't need people like me;

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:02.110
you need the Spirit of the Lord inside

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:03.430
of

00:07:03.440 --> 00:07:05.990
you. The

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.510
moment you confess Jesus Christ as your

00:07:08.520 --> 00:07:11.030
Lord and Savior, you are wall-to-wall

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:13.270
Holy Spirit; He dwells inside of

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:14.950
you.

00:07:14.960 --> 00:07:16.909
It's all by

00:07:16.909 --> 00:07:16.919
grace—something

00:07:16.919 --> 00:07:18.670
you don't earn and don't

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:20.350
deserve.

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:22.470
I want to emphasize that

00:07:22.480 --> 00:07:23.550
tonight

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:26.110
as we pray and show you things

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:28.790
in the news that we believe

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:30.630
the Lord showed us

00:07:30.630 --> 00:07:30.640
previously.

00:07:30.640 --> 00:07:32.990
We have the clips to

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:34.870
show you that we said it before it was in

00:07:34.880 --> 00:07:37.470
the news. The Lord said

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:39.909
if you're chasing the news and

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:41.630
praying what you

00:07:41.630 --> 00:07:41.640
see there,

00:07:41.640 --> 00:07:43.830
you're already too late.

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:46.270
You must pray what's coming, and

00:07:46.270 --> 00:07:46.280
He’ll

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:47.910
show you before it's on

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:50.150
the news. We believe the news

00:07:50.150 --> 00:07:50.160
follows

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:52.470
us because

00:07:52.470 --> 00:07:52.480
we are

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:55.670
led by the Spirit of God.

00:07:58.280 --> 00:07:59.790
When you're led by the Spirit,

00:08:00.880 --> 00:08:04.150
He'll show you that which is to come.

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:06.470
So, I want to encourage you to

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:08.470
keep on keeping on.

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:10.510
Even when the waves of life try to knock

00:08:10.520 --> 00:08:11.830
you down,

00:08:11.840 --> 00:08:13.630
you're not moved by what

00:08:13.640 --> 00:08:15.030
you see

00:08:15.030 --> 00:08:15.040
or

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:16.350
feel; you're moved by what the Word of

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:17.630
God says.

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:21.310
If you feel you've

00:08:21.320 --> 00:08:23.430
missed it

00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:23.440
or

00:08:23.440 --> 00:08:24.750
been

00:08:24.760 --> 00:08:27.270
derailed

00:08:27.270 --> 00:08:27.280
by

00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:29.990
wrong

00:08:29.990 --> 00:08:30.000
choices—marrying

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:32.070
the wrong girl or the wrong man, taking

00:08:32.070 --> 00:08:32.080
the wrong

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:34.350
job, or

00:08:34.350 --> 00:08:34.360
moving

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:36.469
into

00:08:38.350 --> 00:08:38.360
the

00:08:41.990 --> 00:08:42.000
wrong

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:45.950
house—the

00:08:49.520 --> 00:08:51.390
steps of the righteous are ordered

00:08:51.400 --> 00:08:53.270
of the Lord. The Lord said to me

00:08:53.280 --> 00:08:55.150
specifically one night when I was really

00:08:55.160 --> 00:08:57.270
upset about my daughter's reaction

00:08:57.270 --> 00:08:57.280
to a

00:08:57.280 --> 00:08:59.750
vaccination,

00:09:01.430 --> 00:09:01.440
blaming

00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:07.270
myself

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:09.750
for

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:12.510
the big mistake I thought

00:09:12.510 --> 00:09:12.520
I had

00:09:12.520 --> 00:09:15.110
made.

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:16.870
And he said, 'Brandon,

00:09:16.880 --> 00:09:18.470
you're not big enough to derail your

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:19.750
life.

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:21.750
The footsteps of the righteous are

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.230
ordered of me.

00:09:23.240 --> 00:09:25.270
And if you're looking to me and you're

00:09:25.280 --> 00:09:27.950
keeping your eyes on me, what the devil

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:29.670
meant for bad, I'll turn it around for

00:09:29.680 --> 00:09:31.430
good in your favor.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:34.310
All you have to do is seek me, and I'll

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.030
turn what the devil meant for bad,

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:38.510
Brandon, good for

00:09:38.510 --> 00:09:38.520
you.'The

00:09:38.520 --> 00:09:40.350
footsteps of the righteous are

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:42.270
ordered of the Lord.

00:09:42.280 --> 00:09:44.190
And so I want you to be encouraged

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:46.510
tonight that you're not big enough to

00:09:46.520 --> 00:09:49.310
derail your life.

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:52.590
If you are seeking him, what the devil

00:09:52.600 --> 00:09:54.830
meant for bad in your life, no matter

00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:56.350
what you did, no matter what you've

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:58.110
done,

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:01.350
God will turn it around on a dime. If you

00:10:01.350 --> 00:10:01.360
are

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:04.590
just seeking him, there

00:10:04.590 --> 00:10:04.600
is no

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:07.430
sin

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.630
big enough to keep you away from

00:10:09.640 --> 00:10:11.430
the love of God.

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:13.910
There's not sin enough to keep you away

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:16.470
from heaven. As long as you confess your

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:18.750
sins, he is faithful and just to forgive

00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:21.110
you of your sins and cleanse you of all

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:23.190
unrighteousness.

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:26.350
The only sin that I see in the

00:10:26.360 --> 00:10:29.390
scripture that's not forgiven is

00:10:29.390 --> 00:10:29.400
blasphemy

00:10:29.400 --> 00:10:33.870
of the Holy Spirit.

00:10:33.880 --> 00:10:35.310
Other than that,

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:37.550
he'll forgive you.

00:10:37.560 --> 00:10:40.790
So, we just keep our eyes on Jesus.

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:42.350
We just keep our eyes on him and we

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:45.310
remain strong.

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.070
So, don't get worried about your

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:50.030
past. Always look to him because he has

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:51.990
you in the palm of his hand and he has

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:53.990
your future.

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:55.910
And what the devil meant for bad, keep

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.910
thinking that: what the devil meant for

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.710
bad to derail my life, God's going to

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:02.510
turn it around for good.

00:11:02.520 --> 00:11:05.430
I don't care what you've done.

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:07.310
You say, 'Well, I used to be homosexual.

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:09.990
I was this. I was that.'God will turn

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:13.829
it around.

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:15.670
He's an ever-present help in a time of

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:17.950
need, and he will forgive you and wash

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:19.870
you in his precious blood. The moment you

00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:21.990
confess him as Lord and Savior and say,

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:24.470
'Lord, here am I. Use me. Do something

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:27.150
with this

00:11:27.150 --> 00:11:27.160
life.'I

